%% Sequenzdiagramm: Event anlegen
%% Erstellt: 2026-04-21
%% Beschreibung: Fluss beim Anlegen eines neuen Events über das UI.

sequenceDiagram
    actor User as Event Office
    participant UI as Web UI
    participant API as Hono API
    participant App as Application
    participant Repo as EventRepository
    participant Audit as AuditRepository
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    User->>UI: Formular ausfüllen + submit
    UI->>API: POST /events (JSON, Cookie)
    API->>API: requireAuth + requireRole(event_office/manager/admin)
    API->>API: zod validate (createEventSchema)
    API->>App: createEvent(input, actorId)
    App->>App: validate endAt > startAt
    App->>Repo: insert events
    Repo->>DB: INSERT events …
    DB-->>Repo: row
    App->>Audit: record(event.created, before=null, after=event)
    Audit->>DB: INSERT audit_records …
    App-->>API: Event
    API-->>UI: 201 { event }
    UI->>UI: invalidate ["events"]
    UI->>User: navigate /events/:id
